data.description: Welcome to this wonderful 2 bed, 2 bath condo located in the desirable and pet friendly Society Hill section of Basking Ridge. In this beautiful community, residents are offered an abundance of amenities including inground pool, tennis courts, clubhouse, playgrounds and walking paths. This condo's second floor, end unit location provides plenty of privacy and overlooks a peaceful wooded area which you can enjoy while sipping your morning coffee or tea on the balcony. The open concept layout features cathedral ceilings and skylights in the living room and a beautiful kitchen with separate dining area. The primary bedroom allows in plenty of natural light, features an en suite bathroom and a walk-in closet with plenty of storage space. The secondary bedroom offers plenty of closet/storage space as well. Great location for commuters; close to 78, 287, 202, and conveniently located close to shopping malls, dining and blue ribbon schools make this one you'll want to see today!
